{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-060","title":"美味水果","sectionId":"chapter-03","sectionTitle":"美食餐饮全收录","pageStart":321,"pageEnd":325,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":9,"duplicateEntryCount":27,"pages":[{"number":321,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"60 美味水果"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"apple [ˈæpl]","headword":"apple"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.苹果"},{"type":"note","text":"◎apple butter苹果果酱/rotten apple讨厌的家伙"},{"type":"entry","text":"apple of one's eyes掌上明珠","headword":"apple of one's eyes"},{"type":"entry","text":"banana [bəˈnɑːnə]","headword":"banana"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.香蕉"},{"type":"note","text":"◎banana split香蕉圣代/big banana大人物"},{"type":"entry","text":"pear [peə(r)]","headword":"pear"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.梨"},{"type":"note","text":"◎balsam pear苦瓜/prickly pear仙人掌"},{"type":"entry","text":"orange [ˈɒrɪndʒ]","headword":"orange"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.橙；柑；橘子"},{"type":"note","text":"◎orange peel陈皮；橙皮；橘皮"},{"type":"entry","text":"grape [ɡreɪp]","headword":"grape"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.葡萄，提子"},{"type":"note","text":"◎grape jelly葡萄果冻/a bunch of grapes一串葡萄"}]},{"number":322,"blocks":[]},{"number":323,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"sugar cane 甘蔗","headword":"sugar cane"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sugar cane juice甘蔗汁"}]},{"number":324,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"kiwi fruit 猕猴桃；奇异果","headword":"kiwi fruit"},{"type":"note","text":"◎kiwi fruit jam猕猴桃果酱"}]},{"number":325,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"passion fruit 百香果","headword":"passion fruit"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"水果也疯狂"},{"type":"text","text":"1. Banana除了“香蕉”之意，还可以用banana-head来表示“笨蛋，傻"},{"type":"text","text":"瓜”，banana还可以指ABC（American Born Chinese），即指那些虽有"},{"type":"text","text":"着中国人的黄皮肤，可在价值观、生活习惯等方面都完全西化的美国"},{"type":"text","text":"人。bananas还有个特别的意思，就是指“发疯”，它等同于nuts或"},{"type":"text","text":"crazy。例如：She is driving me bananas.（她使我发疯。）Go bananas"},{"type":"text","text":"意为“发怒，发疯，发傻”。"},{"type":"text","text":"2. Lemon还可以指“无用的东西，蹩脚货（尤指汽车），废物；蠢"},{"type":"text","text":"人，无用的人”，hand sb. a lemon指“把蹩脚的东西给某人”，就是“让"},{"type":"text","text":"某人不快”的意思。柠檬法（Lemon Law）是美国的一种消费者保护"},{"type":"text","text":"法，主要用于保障汽车买主的权益。出厂后有瑕疵的汽车，通常被称"},{"type":"text","text":"为lemon car或lemon。"}]}]}